reviewText: A laugh a minute about the Espanol families. Great DVD.
Excelente pelcula, reconocidos actores mexicanos de larga trayectoria. Fue para un regalo y gust muchsimo. Buen vendedor. Lo recomiendo 100%.
Loved this movie! It's so hilarious! I'm so happy that I bought this, and I do recommend it. Buy it!

This movie is probably never going to win an Oscar, but it is a very entertainig and funny film. I'm mexican, but I have been raised in America, and this film makes me remember every time we go back to Mexico, because sometimes we have to face some stupid and funny situations
